# Walkthrough - Phase 21: SetList Panel Redesign

I have redesigned the SetList panel's bottom toolbar to feature a high-density, professional segmented control layout with two horizontal bars.

## Changes Made

### 1. Data Models & Persistence
- **[setlist_item.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/setlist/data/setlist_item.dart)**: Added `isFavorite` property and `copyWith` support to all setlist item types.
- **[saved_setlist.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/setlist/data/saved_setlist.dart)**: Added a `favorites` list to persist the favorite status in Isar.
- **[setlist_repository.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/setlist/data/setlist_repository.dart)**: Updated save/load logic to handle the new favorite status.

### 2. State Management
- **[setlist_providers.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/setlist/presentation/setlist_providers.dart)**: Added `toggleFavorite` method to the `SetlistNotifier` to batch-toggle favorites for selected items.

### 3. UI Implementation
- **[setlist_pane.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/dashboard/presentation/widgets/setlist_pane.dart)**:
    - **Segmented Control**: Replaced the previous `Wrap`-based toolbar with two fixed-height (20px) rows.
    - **3D Styling**: Implemented a `_segmentedButton` helper with silver gradients, thin vertical separators, and a stacked icon effect to simulate an "engraved" look.
    - **Favorite Indicators**: SetList items now display a small amber star icon if they are marked as favorites.
    - **Handlers**:
        - **Delete/Move/Save**: Ported to the new layout.
        - **Clear All**: Added a confirmation dialog.
        - **Favorite**: Added logic to mark/unmark selected items.
        - **Refresh**: Added a placeholder snackbar.

## Verification Results

- **Layout**: Two bars of 4 buttons each, occupying full width at the bottom of the panel.
- **Interaction**:
    - Multi-select items and click the Star icon -> Star appears next to items.
    - Click "Clear All" -> Dialog appears.
    - Click "Refresh" -> Snackbar appears.
    - Click "Save" -> Favorite status is persisted to the database.
- **Styling**: Silver/Gray gradient backgrounds with subtle 3D depth and centered monochrome icons.

> [!TIP]
> Hover over the icons to see the tooltips as labels are intentionally omitted to maintain the high-density professional look.
